    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> in 100ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [125ml]  </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>mustard stock</strong></p>",
