    {
      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze the pouch[es] of<strong> steamed brown basmati rice</strong> to separate the grains</p><p>Tear the top corner of the pouch[es] (just a little!) and <strong>microwave</strong> for 2 min or until piping hot</p><p>Tip: If you're cooking two pouches, pop them in together but increase the microwave cook time accordingly</p><p>Trim, then chop your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p>",
