    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crumble your <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> into the pan and cook for a further 2 min</p><p>Add your<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong> and cook for 30 secs further</p><p>Add your <strong>mustard</strong> <strong>stock</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
